726832f-b.title: Queens: Greenpoint Avenue - 37th Street
726832f-b.text:
(1)
Greenpoint Avenue, south side, east from 37th Street.
The new apartmentiunder construction, seen in the back-
ground, is near 39th Place.
July 27, 1940
P. L. Sperr
(2)
Greenpoint Avenue, at 50th Avenue (right), showing
Mnew type attached dwellings and the seven-story apartment
house.
July 27, 1940
P. L. Sperr
